        "message": "=Hey {{ $('Lookup client FirstName and email').item.json.FirstName }}, \n<br>\nyour campaign <strong>{{ $('Get SL lead details').item.json.lead_campaign_data[0].campaign_name }}</strong> has received a reply from a lead.        \n  <br><br>                                                                                                                                                        \n  <strong>Here's the data:</strong>                               \n  <br><br>\n  First Name: {{ $('Get SL lead details').item.json.first_name }}<br>\n  Last Name: {{ $('Get SL lead details').item.json.last_name }}<br>                                                                                               \n  Company Name: {{ $('Get SL lead details').item.json.company_name }}<br>\n  Email: {{ $('Get SL lead details').item.json.email }}<br>                                                                                                       \n  Company website: {{ $('Get SL lead details').item.json.website }}<br>\n  Reply AI category: {{ {1: 'Interested', 2: 'Meeting Request', 3: 'Not Interested', 5: 'Information Request', 8: 'Uncategorizable by AI'}[$('Get SL lead details').item.json.lead_campaign_data[0].lead_category_id] }}                                                                                                  \n  <br><br>                                                                                                                                                        \n  <strong>{{ $('Get SL lead details').item.json.first_name }} {{ $('Get SL lead details').item.json.last_name }} replied:</strong>                                \n  <br><br>                                                                              <div style=\"background-color:#fef9e7; border-left:2px solid #f0b429; padding:12px; margin:8px 0;\">                                                                          \n  {{ $('Clean HTML reply').item.json.reply }}                                           </div>                                                                             \n  <br><br>                                                                                                                                                        \n  <strong>to the following our message (which was no {{ $('Clean HTML reply').item.json.seq_number }} in sequence):</strong>                                      \n  <br><br>                                                                              <div style=\"background-color:#fef9e7; border-left:2px solid #f0b429; padding:12px; margin:8px 0;\">                                                 \n  {{ $('Clean HTML reply').item.json.last_sent }}\n</div>  \n  <br><br>                                                                                                                                                        \n   <strong>Proceed with the lead now.</strong>                                     \n  <br><br>                                                                                                                                                        \n  Questions, comments, need a call prep? Reply to this message.   \n  <br><br>                                                                                                                                                        \n  Thanks much,<br><br>                                                \n  --<br>                                                                                                                                                          \n  Best regards,<br>                                               \n  Egor Pravilov<br>                                                                                                                                               \n  SharpDMA | Precision outbound<br>\n  sharpdma.com<br>                                                                                  